[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第二",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "卿傳梵大師賜紫沙門臣法護等奉　詔譯爾時，復有無數百千夜叉之眾，雨諸蓮華而伸供養，又復吹擊和風觸者安樂。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有無數諸佛剎中彼彼如來，為供養世尊釋迦牟尼佛及正法故，各從眉間放大光明。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其光具有青、黃、赤、白、紅頗胝迦，及翡翠等種種之色及種種相，種種光明右繞於此三千大千世界，普遍照耀，而悉除破一切暗冥，光復旋還繞象頭山，後從世尊頂門而入。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有無數百千婆羅門、剎帝利、士庶人民，各持香花塗香末香，眾妙花鬘衣服幢幡及諸寶蓋，置於佛前以伸供養。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當佛宣說如是正法，及諸天龍神獻供養時，有七十二那庾多菩薩得無生法忍。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無數百千俱胝那庾多有情，遠塵離垢得法眼淨。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無數百千俱胝那庾多有情，先未曾發菩提心者，皆發無上大菩提心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，有一天女名曰長壽，久住於此象頭山中，與自眷屬先在佛會。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750a28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即從座起，為供養佛故往自宮中，取諸供養還來詣佛，到佛所已尊重恭敬，專諦一心獻諸供養。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是至誠作供養已。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "前白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我知過去久久生中，有七萬二千諸佛、如來。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉曾於此象頭山中說此正法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦如是義、亦如是理、亦如是文。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b04_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長壽天女！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝快得善利，值遇如是法寶出世，一一親聞。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，會中有諸天子咸作是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此天女，久已曾聞如是正法，復曾親近多佛、如來，何故不能轉此女身？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，除蓋障菩薩知諸天子心所念已，白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因何緣，此長壽天女具大威德，久已曾聞如是正法，復曾親近多佛如來，何故不轉此女人身？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b12_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不轉女身者，廣為利樂一切有情大因緣故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今此天女已住不可思議解脫菩薩之位。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我知此長壽天女，曾於超過算數諸如來所，勸請發菩提心，乃至入大涅槃。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b16_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是緣故，而此天女獲是廣大神通威德。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此長壽天女，即於賢劫中供養諸佛已，此佛剎中當得成佛，號曰長壽如來、應供、正等正覺。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告長壽天女言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今應現自佛國土莊嚴之事。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，長壽天女即入現一切色相三摩地。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是三摩地中，現此三千大千世界地平如掌，除去黑山土石山等，及餘一切本有樹木，清淨可愛琉璃所成。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "處處皆有妙劫波樹，處處皆有清淨嚴好泉源池沼，八功德水充滿其中，除去一切凡常人類，亦復不聞女人之聲。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "處處皆現廣大蓮花，其一一花量如車輪，諸蓮花中有菩薩像加趺而坐。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750b29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復現世尊長壽如來、應供、正等正覺，與諸菩薩共會說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有無數百千俱胝那庾多帝釋、梵王、護世天等之所圍繞，又有無數百千俱胝那庾多菩薩之眾圍繞聽法，所謂亦說如是法門。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，長壽天女如是現已，即從三摩地起，於世尊前，右繞三匝隱而不現。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，除蓋障菩薩前白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人於此正法，聽聞受持讀誦記念解釋其義，復為他人廣大說者，是人得幾所福？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正使三千大千世界，滿中有情悉行布施，經無量時相續不斷。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，於此正法發清淨心，如法書寫復善詳校，又以淨心轉施於他，是人所獲福德倍勝於前。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫財施者不出生死，而法施者最上最勝。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切有情在生死中，貪受種種財利事故，不能受彼最上法味出於世間。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正使有人，以此三千大千世界滿中有情，悉令安住十善業道。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人，於此正法，聽聞受持讀誦記念解釋其義，復為他人廣大說者，是人所獲福德倍勝於前。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十善業道，從是正法所出生故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正使三千大千世界滿中有情，悉令證得須陀洹果、斯陀含果、阿那含果、阿羅漢果。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人於此正法，聽聞受持讀誦記念解釋其義，復為他人廣大說者，是人所獲福德倍勝於前。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知一切聲聞緣覺，皆悉從是法性中來；",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩者，亦悉從是法性中來；",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0750c29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來亦得是法性故出現世間。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人能於如是正法，受持讀誦解其義者，是人即同於諸經中受持讀誦解釋義趣。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法性者是諸法母。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而諸菩薩若不得此正法性者，即不能得廣大法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，會中諸大聲聞，各從座起偏袒右肩，右膝著地，俱白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等獲得此法性已，而能普盡廣大生死邪？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸苾芻！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊普告在會諸大眾言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸地方有能宣說如是正法之處，而彼地方當知即是大菩提場，即是轉法輪處，即是大靈塔處，當起是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『是我大師所遊止處。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a13_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法性即是菩提，即是轉法輪，法輪即是如來。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若供養法者，是即供養諸佛如來。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸地方有說法師所遊止處，當於彼地起靈塔想，於說法師起大師想。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復當起善知識想，又應當起善導師想。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故，若時見彼說法師已，當起淨信歡喜之心，尊重恭敬承迎於前，稱揚讚嘆白言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我若讚說尊重恭敬法師功德，及說報其法師大恩，如是等事，若經一劫，若過一劫，我亦不能說其少分。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有愛樂法者，諸善男子及善女人，於說法師所履道中，以自身血散灑其地，亦不能報彼說法師少分恩德。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說法師者，以能任持如來法眼，極難行故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故諸說法師，當說如是正法之時，應現無畏，不應沈下生障礙心，著新淨衣起清淨心。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751a29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當說法時，若人讚嘆不起高心，不現我相不生慢執，不自稱譽不凌毀他，亦復不生染著之心，應當恭敬尊重說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，帝釋天主前白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸地方有說如是正法之處，我當率諸宮屬往詣彼所，聽受如是甚深正法，及為護助彼說法師。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝善守護如來正法，如汝所作今正是時。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此經何名？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等云何奉持？",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是經名曰『除蓋障菩薩所問』，亦名『寶雲』，亦名『寶積功德』，亦名『智燈』，如是名字汝當受持。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說此經已，除蓋障菩薩等，彼諸菩薩摩訶薩眾，并在會菩薩聲聞之眾，帝釋、梵王、護世諸天、大自在天子等，無數百千諸天子眾，及餘無數百千天、龍、夜叉、乾闥婆、阿修羅、迦樓羅、緊那羅、摩睺羅伽、人、非人等一切大眾，聞佛所說歡喜信受。",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第二十",
        "from": "T14n0489_020:0751b19_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]